title: Sailor Moon Memorial Song Box
description:
Sailor Moon Memorial Song Box comprises all songs from the famous TV series.

Disc 1: TV Series Best Song Collection
Disc 2: Bishoujo Senshi Sailormoon Song Collection
Disc 3: Bishoujo Senshi Sailormoon R Song Collection + Best Movie Collection
Disc 4: Bishoujo Senshi Sailormoon Sailorstars Song Collection
Disc 5: Bishoujo Senshi Sailormoon Sailorstars Poem & Prologue Collection
Disc 6: Bishoujo Senshi Sailormoon Original Karaoke Best Collection


All audio files in Musepack ~230 kbps + cover art.
